# File Naming Conventions

- All component files should use dash-case naming convention
  - ✅ `auth-button.tsx`
  - ❌ `AuthButton.tsx`
  - ✅ `delete-chat-button.tsx`
  - ❌ `DeleteChatButton.tsx`

- All files should use TypeScript (.ts/.tsx) instead of JavaScript (.js/.jsx)
  - ✅ `component.tsx`
  - ❌ `component.jsx`
  - ✅ `utils.ts`
  - ❌ `utils.js`

Components should be placed in the [components](mdc:src/components) directory.
